OL,3,CCondor ferry diverts journey after
OL,4,CFrench yacht mayday call
OL,6,FThe RNLI has thanked crew of the
OL,7,FCondor Voyager for diverting its
OL,8,Fjourney to save those aboard a French
OL,9,Fyacht after its skipper was taken ill
OL,10,Feight miles off Jersey's south-west
OL,11,Fcoast.
OL,13,FFollowing a distress call from the
OL,14,Fskipper's daughters shortly after
OL,15,F6:30pm yesterday, the St Malo-bound
OL,16,FCondor Voyager offered assistance to
OL,17,Fthe RNLI team as they tackled a heavy
OL,18,Fswell and force six winds during the
OL,19,Frescue.
