OL,3,CCondor ferry diverts journey after
OL,4,CFrench yacht mayday call
OL,6,FCondor crew launched their rescue boat
OL,7,Fand helped the RNLI provide immediate
OL,8,Fcare for the skipper while also
OL,9,Fassessing an issue with the yacht's
OL,10,Fforesail.
OL,12,FDespite being unable to transfer the
OL,13,Fstricken skipper to the RNLI's all-
OL,14,Fweather boat due to the rough sea
OL,15,Fconditions, the skipper and those on
OL,16,Fboard the yacht were guided back to St
OL,17,FHelier under a reduced sail area,
OL,18,Farriving at around 10pm.
