OL,6,FThe Condor Voyager then continued its
OL,7,Fjourney to St Malo after it was
OL,8,Fdecided that the yacht's skipper was
OL,9,Fwell enough to travel.
OL,11,FGibby Gordon, Coxswain for RNLI
OL,12,FJersey, said: "This was a great
OL,13,Fexample of multiple vessels working
OL,14,Ftogether to help manage a mayday
OL,15,Fsituation.
OL,17,F"We are extremely grateful to Condor
OL,18,FVoyager and her crew who were first on
OL,19,Fscene and able to provide immediate
OL,20,Fassistance.
